msgid "‘ahaṃ, bhante, pāpakammaṃ akāsiṃ gārayhaṃ upavajjaṃ."
msgstr "‘Sirs, I’ve done a bad and reprehensible deed, deserving of criticism."

msgctxt "an4.244:4.3"
msgid "Yena me āyasmanto attamanā honti taṃ karomī’ti."
msgstr "I submit to your pleasure.’"

