"tibbā bhayasaññā paccupaṭṭhitā hoti pāṭidesanīyesu dhammesu, tassetaṃ "
"pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—anāpanno vā pāṭidesanīyaṃ dhammaṃ na āpajjissati, āpanno vā "
"pāṭidesanīyaṃ dhammaṃ yathādhammaṃ paṭikarissati."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, take any monk or nun who has set up such an acute "
"perception of peril regarding confession offenses. It can be expected that "
"if they haven’t committed a confession offense they won’t, and if they "
"committed one they will deal with it properly."

msgctxt "an4.244:4.11"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri āpattibhayānī”ti."
msgstr "These are the four perils of offenses.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.244:4.12"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
